name: Study Association Sirius
position 1: Study Association for Health Sciences, Management, Society & Technology and Public Administration
summary:
Sirius is the Study Association for the bachelor studies Management, Society & Technology and Gezondheidswetenschappen (Health Sciences) and the master studies Public Administration, European Studies and Health Sciences. Our students solve societal problems from a technological angle. 

Throughout the academic year Sirius organises various activities, such as lunch lectures, our annual Symposium, or our annual Career Day. 

Are you interested to get in touch with our students, by for example reaching them digitally, or by participating in one of our activities? Send an e-mail to Sirius via extern@siriusenschede.nl or call 053 489 3204.
